## SERP ANALYSIS

**Competitor Summary:**
- Word count range: 800–2,400 words (avg: ~1,400)
- Most ranking pages are thin editorial pieces (Country & Town House, The List, Elowell Max) — minimal depth, no audience insight, no shape guidance, no seasonal nuance
